From: =?UTF-8?q?Christian=20K=C3=B6nig?= <christian.koenig@amd.com>

commit b7d698d7fd7d132c6ebe56d230584f2cae6c94ee upstream.

mem->start is a long, so this can overflow on 32bit systems.

